name: Who will win the fight Kata
description:
Who will win the fight Kata
---

Two people decide that they want to fight. If someones name starts with a "z", it means that they will win the fight.

----------------

Return the name of the winner. Unless...

If both their names start with a "z", return "tie".

If neither their names start with a "z", return "tie".

----------------

THINGS TO NOTE:

You will never be given any empty names or null values.

Names will always be fully lower case.
